data.description: This beautiful home boast as 4 br with study or a 5br. Bright and open living space with large living/ family room and dining area. The spacious kitchen looks into the living room, perfect for cooking and entertainment. It has beautiful stain and steel appliances double ovens, granite counters, island and breakfast bar. Downstairs also feature a home office. Upstairs you'll have an enormous loft/entertainment room. The oversize master separate tub and shower, his and her separate granite sink, extra-large garden tub, and massive walk-in closet. Backyard perfect for entertainment. NO HOA. This gem is perfect for those seeking convenience.  Location is close proximity to schools and 7 mins from restaurants, shopping, and nestled comfortably in cul-de-sac.
